description:
This is a 30 minute workout called '30 MIN FULL BODY WORKOUT || At-Home Beginner Pilates (No Equipment)' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates and Cardio/Mat.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Moderate.
